(firstQuint)The Efficacy and Safety of Fang yi Qing Feng Shi Granules in Subjects With Rheumatoid Arthritis.

 Fang yi qing feng shi granules is the chinese patent medicine, which contains 8 kinds of chinese medicine .

 Fang yi qing feng shi granules was approved by China Food and Drug Administration (CFDA) in 2005, produced by means of modern technology by Maoxiang Group Jilin Pharmaceutical Co.

, Ltd.

The study is a multi-center, double -blind, placebo -controlled, randomized in Chinese subjects with Rheumatoid Arthritis to assess treatment effect and safety in the subjects treated with Fang yi qing feng shi granules versus subjects treated with placebo.

